folder: Prince Street & Concord Street, Brooklyn, NY
text:
Prince Street, south from near Concord Street, showing demolition of buildings. Part of this area was incorporated into the Fort Greene Houses development.

View 1 shows several remaining rookeries at Tillary Street.

September 6, 1939
Views 1,2

P. L. Sperr
